{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168432688","path":null,"data":{"id":1642,"title":"AIA:更新「AIA自願醫保計劃」系列醫院釋義","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1676946849128,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #f50045;\">由2023年4月1日起，</span></strong>AIA將按照醫務衞生局要求，於所有<strong><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">「AIA自願醫保計劃」</span></strong>系列保單條款及細則內釐清「醫院」的釋義，列明包括位於香港並屬於《醫院管理局條例》所界定的公營醫院或是根據《私營醫療機構條例》領有牌照的醫院。<strong><span style=\"color: #f50045;\">是次更新無須額外保費</span></strong>，而認可產品編號亦將維持不變。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-02-21/5dfb308ccf834c9cb4dd7b174b649918.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Memo.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-21/b64d042fcee5422580b0676a92cfa766.pdf","uploadTime":1676945377216,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:AVPP","AIA:AVHIPS","AIA:AVP","AIA:AVS","AIA:AVF"],"productNames":["AIA自願醫保尊裕計劃","AIA自願醫保尊顯計劃","AIA自願醫保尊尚計劃","AIA自願醫保標準計劃","AIA自願醫保靈活計劃"],"companyCodes":["AIA"],"companyNames":["友邦保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1680314490432,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}